=Characteristics=

"Framed Democracy has outlined the core values of Democracy 2.0 as:

1. Being led by the will of the people (always and on all policy areas)

2. An informed constituency

3. Transparency 

4. Accountability

5. No corporate donations

6. Truth is found in facts

7. Leadership mea culpa

8. Equality of opportunity & Meritocracy

9. A secular commitment


